itemMetadata.name: Mirror of Kalandra
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click an equipable non-unique item to apply it. Mirrored copies cannot be modified.
effect: Creates a Mirrored copy of an item

itemMetadata.name: Divine Orb
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click an item to apply it.
effect: Randomises the numeric values of modifiers on an item

itemMetadata.name: Orb of Annulment
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click on a magic or rare item to apply it.
effect: Removes a random modifier from an item

itemMetadata.name: Fracturing Orb
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a rare item to apply it. Cannot be used on Fractured items.
effect: Fracture a random modifier on a rare item with at least 4 modifiers, locking it in place.

itemMetadata.name: Perfect Jeweller's Orb
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a Skill Gem to apply it. Can only apply to Skill Gems with fewer than 5 Support Gem Sockets.
effect: Sets a Skill Gem to have 5 Support Gem Sockets

itemMetadata.name: Orb of Chance
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a normal item to apply it.
effect: Unpredictably either upgrades a Normal item to Unique rarity or destroys it

itemMetadata.name: Chaos Orb
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a rare item to apply it.
effect: Removes a random modifier and augments a Rare item with a new random modifier

itemMetadata.name: Chance Shard
itemMetadata.description: A stack of 10 shards becomes an Orb of Chance.

itemMetadata.name: Vaal Orb
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click an item to corrupt it. Corrupted items cannot be modified again.
effect: Modifies an item unpredictably and Corrupts it

itemMetadata.name: Exalted Orb
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a rare item to apply it. Rare items can have up to six random modifiers.
effect: Augments a Rare item with a new random modifier

itemMetadata.name: Artificer's Shard
itemMetadata.description: A stack of 10 shards becomes an Artificer's Orb.

itemMetadata.name: Arcanist's Etcher
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a wand, staff or sceptre to apply it. The maximum quality is 20%.
effect: Improves the quality of a wand, staff or sceptre

itemMetadata.name: Regal Shard
itemMetadata.description: A stack of 10 shards becomes a Regal Orb.

itemMetadata.name: Regal Orb
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a magic item to apply it. Current modifiers are retained and a new one is added.
effect: Upgrades a Magic item to a Rare item, adding 1 modifier

itemMetadata.name: Transmutation Shard
itemMetadata.description: A stack of 10 shards becomes an Orb of Transmutation

itemMetadata.name: Gemcutter's Prism
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a skill gem to apply it. The maximum quality is 20%.
effect: Improves the quality of a skill gem

itemMetadata.name: Glassblower's Bauble
itemMetadata.description: Right click this item then left click a flask to apply it. The maximum quality is 20%.
effect: Improves the quality of a flask
